\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Component ablation: mean forgetting $\pm $ std across 5 seeds. Governor-only tracks SGD, confirming LR modulation alone is insufficient. Penalty-only accounts for the majority of the forgetting reduction. The full TCL vs.\ penalty-only gap ($\Delta = 0.016$) is directional but not resolved at $n=5$ ($p = 0.315$, $d = 0.51$). }}{9}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:ablation}{{2}{9}{Component ablation: mean forgetting $\pm $ std across 5 seeds. Governor-only tracks SGD, confirming LR modulation alone is insufficient. Penalty-only accounts for the majority of the forgetting reduction. The full TCL vs.\ penalty-only gap ($\Delta = 0.016$) is directional but not resolved at $n=5$ ($p = 0.315$, $d = 0.51$)}{figure.2}{}}
