\newlabel{tab:tinyimagenet}{{5}{9}{Split-TinyImageNet scale-up. Forgetting and accuracy are mean $\pm $ std over 3 seeds. $p$ and $d$ are paired $t$-test (two-tailed) of TCL vs.\ each baseline}{table.5}{}}
